{"type":"message","id":"d3bc5632","parentId":"da2d6d2a","timestamp":"2026-05-09T07:28:23.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user shared a Douyin (TikTok China) link. Douyin videos typically can't be fetched directly via web_fetch. The message is in Chinese and references \"美客多\", \"跨境电商\", \"ai选品\", \"accio\" - these seem to be about cross-border e-commerce and AI product selection tools.\n\nThe sender is ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 (looks like a Feishu user ID).\n\nThe message content says \"8.48 复制打开抖音，看看【聂风有话说的作品】# 美客多# 跨境电商# ai选品# accio#...\" which translates roughly to \"8.48 copy and open Douyin to see [Nie Feng has something to say's work] # Mekedo # cross-border e-commerce # ai product selection # accio#...\"\n\nThis seems like a random shared Douyin video link, not something that requires action from me. The user might have accidentally shared it or shared it without context. I should acknowledge it but also note I can't view Douyin video content.\n\nThe conversation is direct (DM), so I should reply naturally. Given the context, I'll respond acknowledging the shared link and noting I can't access Douyin content directly.\n","thinkingSignature":"c26916ca82e275dd0cce34c4b3fcce405ce130e11054d82ec646caa765f9ee49"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到了一个抖音链接，但 Douyin 的视频内容我没办法直接抓取来看 😅\n\n看起来是关于「美客多 / 跨境电商 / AI选品 / accio」的内容，和电商选品相关？\n\n如果你想聊这个话题，可以简单描述一下视频说了啥，或者问你想了解什么，我来帮你查！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":155,"output":331,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778311690676,"responseId":"064e150a76d386120dbe3119fba18ebd"}}
