{"type":"message","id":"f07e23f3","parentId":"2f4fe333","timestamp":"2026-05-09T07:28:42.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about whether we still need to use the MCP (Model Context Protocol) workflow, given that they've found a browser visualization collection process that works. They seem to be comparing two approaches:\n\n1. A browser visualization/crawling approach shown in the Douyin video\n2. MCP-based workflows\n\nLet me think about this. The user seems to be working on some kind of data collection or web scraping project, and they're evaluating whether to continue using MCP or switch to a browser-based approach.\n\nI don't have context about what their specific MCP setup looks like or what project this is for. I should ask clarifying questions to understand better what they're trying to accomplish and what their current MCP setup does, so I can give a more informed opinion.\n\nThis seems to be a follow-up to some prior work. Let me check memory for context about this project.\n","thinkingSignature":"da10949cdd1b20671d859a9a74b6652c1f649abe0f16493f6a1bf27c6cda0e14"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rsokgq1z3oj9_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"MCP browser collection workflow project"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16692,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16895,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778311708353,"responseId":"064e151c689ea3ca0153c8ad63e5b5b2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1636b5f","parentId":"f07e23f3","timestamp":"2026-05-09T07:28:51.418Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rsokgq1z3oj9_1","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 9110,\n    \"hits\": 0\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","debug":{"backend":"builtin","effectiveMode":"n/a","searchMs":9110,"hits":0}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778311731418}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbb96b77","parentId":"c1636b5f","timestamp":"2026-05-09T07:29:12.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No memory results. Let me think about this from scratch.\n\nThe user is asking about whether to continue using an MCP-based workflow for browser visualization/collection, given that they now see another approach (from the Douyin video) that can also work.\n\nWithout specific context about what the MCP workflow does vs what the browser visualization approach does, I should ask for more context or share general considerations.\n\nActually, let me think about what makes sense:\n1. The MCP approach typically gives structured, programmatic access to browser automation\n2. The \"browser visualization\" approach likely uses a GUI-based tool for visual web scraping/automation\n\nThe trade-offs:\n- MCP: more flexible, scriptable, can be integrated into other workflows\n\n\n- Visual tools: easier to use, faster to set up for simple tasks, but less flexible\n\nI need to understand what the MCP project is actually doing before I can give useful advice on whether to stick with it or pivot.\n","thinkingSignature":"3b0759519dda02bd583ae6cce716fa1eb6edbbdaad920d9dffa23a29ad804e33"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n没有找到之前的项目记录，简单说下我的思路：\n\n**选哪个看场景：**\n\n| | MCP 流程 | 浏览器可视化工具 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **灵活性** | 高，可编程、可串联其他系统 | 低，适合固定流程 |\n| **维护成本** | 代码可控，但需要开发维护 | 拖拽配置，但迁移困难 |\n| **适合复杂/长链路** | ✅ | ❌ |\n| **适合快速验证/单次任务** | ❌ | ✅ |\n\n**我的问题：**\n- 你们现在 MCP 那套跑的是什么场景？采集+后续处理全链路，还是只是采集？\n- 浏览器可视化工具跑通的那个，是单次采集还是也需要定时跑？\n\n如果只是采集环节，两个选一个就行。如果采集之后还有处理/写入/MCP做得好就留着；如果只是采集且流程固定，可视化工具更快。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":219,"output":369,"cacheRead":16576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17164,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778311731419,"responseId":"064e15345cd639fee16fa1478377e3ed"}}
{"type":"message","id":"01452aaf","parentId":"fbb96b77","timestamp":"2026-05-09T08:29:52.612Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b50db490da878b25a97efbd76bc1]\nou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 是这样，就是之前5. 0的整个选品策略计划里边，我们单独摘出了一个数据源获取。\n\n咱们都是有什么呀？简短一点给我"}],"timestamp":1778315392496}}
