{"type":"message","id":"718f85f2","parentId":"4be62046","timestamp":"2026-05-09T08:30:02.140Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"They want a brief list of what data sources we have in the 5.0 product selection strategy project, specifically the data source acquisition part.\n","thinkingSignature":"59b8ea455f99d67193ef02422359416247ea77c6e216ae1b7e7dd3f318527309"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n之前 5.0 选品策略的数据源大概有这几块：\n\n1. **Mercado Libre 平台数据** - 类目、销量、价格、评价\n2. **Google Trends / 搜索热度** - 关键词趋势\n3. **竞品数据** - 竞品 ASIN 的排名、评论、评分\n4. **评论文本** - 用户反馈提取痛点/需求\n5. **第三方工具 API** - 可能是 Jungle Scout、Helium 10 这类\n\n你那边浏览器可视化采集跑通的是哪个？看起来像是替代了某个数据源？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17056,"output":155,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17211,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778315392614,"responseId":"064e2382c74e3ee1bddededd664d0b00"}}
