{"type":"message","id":"a4eabe67","parentId":"9b7370dc","timestamp":"2026-05-09T08:48:00.215Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying if they use \"SofaMCP\" they can get 1688 and TikTok Shop product data. So they're suggesting just using SofaMCP for these two data sources instead of the MCP flow they currently have.\n\nLet me check what SofaMCP is and if there's any existing configuration for it.\n","thinkingSignature":"d3ee8b55f67b68263f9dbe1f250037092d47d2a966e8c6bde264770c6fa73bc0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_asq1ld612twq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/mcp*servers*.json ~/.config/openclaw/mcp*.json 2>/dev/null || openclaw mcp list 2>/dev/null || ls ~/.openclaw/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5874,"output":136,"cacheRead":16896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22906,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778316466678,"responseId":"064e27b3844f5a89cdfb39f8befd34dc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"86ed2ab6","parentId":"a4eabe67","timestamp":"2026-05-09T08:48:03.043Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_asq1ld612twq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Config warnings ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                             │\n│  - plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected;     │\n│    global plugin will be overridden by global plugin                        │\n│    (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)  │\n│                                                                             │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nNo MCP servers configured in /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2779,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Config warnings ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                             │\n│  - plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected;     │\n│    global plugin will be overridden by global plugin                        │\n│    (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)  │\n│                                                                             │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nNo MCP servers configured in /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json.","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778316483042}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c309ad8","parentId":"86ed2ab6","timestamp":"2026-05-09T08:48:21.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is suggesting using a \"SofaMCP\" to get 1688 and TikTok Shop product data. They want to use these two data sources.\n\nSofaMCP is likely a browser-based MCP server that can scrape 1688 and TikTok Shop.\n\nBased on the SOP, the three tracks are:\n1. 主动选品 - TikTok Shop + EchoTik\n2. 跟品 - EchoTik + ERP\n3. 1688 直选\n\nIf SofaMCP can get 1688 + TikTok Shop, that covers track 1 (TikTok Shop part) and track 3 (1688). \n\nThat leaves track 2 (跟品 - which needs EchoTik or ERP for hot-selling items) as the gap. The user wants to go ahead with this approach, so I should support them in moving forward with using SofaMCP for the data sources it can handle.\n","thinkingSignature":"9f99b1b611a1ef158f4d01c176b9a75f8256c91c711292585ed478309c10246a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSofaMCP 覆盖两轨，挺合适的：\n\n- **1688** → 供应链驱动选品（第三轨）\n- **TikTok Shop** → 主动选品（第一轨）\n\n**还缺的一轨是跟品**（EchoTik 热卖榜），不过那个主要是抓爆款跟卖，如果你主攻\"精准选品 + 差异化\"路线，1688 + TikTok Shop 两个够了。\n\n**下一步：**\n1. 装一下 SofaMCP（叫什么名字来着？我帮你配）\n2. 确认它能稳定拿到：商品标题/价格/销量/评分/类目\n3. 对接到评分流程里\n\n你们那个浏览器可视化采集是哪个工具？我帮你看看两个能不能互补，或者直接用 SofaMCP 替代。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":303,"output":353,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23312,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778316483044,"responseId":"064e27c3ae2e203283d60048f8daccda"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f9c1bbd","parentId":"5c309ad8","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:37:50.799Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b50c448682884b4856141e74f926]\nou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: SofaMCP已经安装了。\n\nK过期了，晚上我给你个新K，还是一个100次试用的。我们可以先把这100次都给它跑完，测试一下到底能拿到什么信息，然后选一次试试"}],"timestamp":1778319470684}}
