{"type":"message","id":"d2cc2123","parentId":"fff9243f","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:20:56.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user mentioned \"sorftime mcp\" - this sounds like an MCP server for e-commerce data (likely TikTok/Shopee/Mercado Libre based on the context). Let me just ask the user about it since I can't find it in the system.\n","thinkingSignature":"5e6ca0e0427e00749b68681273f26dd16111d119cfcf812f072560b8312521b7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSorftime MCP 是你们自己搭的还是第三方服务？我这边没找到配置。\n\n它能拿什么数据？TikTok Shop / Shopee / Mercado Libre 都能覆盖吗？\n\n晚上 key 到了可以一起测。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":211,"output":100,"cacheRead":26880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27191,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778322049536,"responseId":"064e3d81477d47e5d8b5662d84662f73"}}
