{"type":"message","id":"fe934f7f","parentId":"a33fe6ff","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:24:51.110Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wg24htytb2ow_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"sorftime-mcp\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok电商平台**指定类目**的类目数据报告\n   *\n   * @param nodeId 类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_category_report(nodeId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊平台上类目产品的特点\n   *\n   * @param productName 查询的类目名称\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function similar_product_feature(productName: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productName\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的类目名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询沃尔玛电商平台上实时热搜关键词榜，按月搜索量排序\n   *\n   * @param rank_min 排名范围起始值（如：1）\n   * @param rank_max 排名范围结束值（如：100）\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\n   */\n  function walmart_keyword_list(rank_min: number, rank_max: number, page?: number);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"rank_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"排名范围起始值（如：1）\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\"\n          },\n          \"rank_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"排名范围结束值（如：100）\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"rank_min\",\n          \"rank_max\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询我的亚马逊平台关键词词库的词\n   *\n   * @param dict? 选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\n   * @param keywordSupportSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function get_favorite_keyword(dict?: string, page?: number, keywordSupportSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"keywordSupportSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询我的沃尔玛平台关键词词库的词\n   *\n   * @param dict? 选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\n   */\n  function walmart_get_favorite_keyword(dict?: string, page?: number);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台上热搜关键词搜索结果自然位产品清单\n   *\n   * @param keyword 查询的关键词\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\n   * @param keywordSupportSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function keyword_search_results(keyword: string, page?: number, keywordSupportSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"keywordSupportSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"keyword\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台细分类目市场趋势数据，基于类目Top100产品统计\n   *\n   * @param nodeId 查询类目的nodeid，数据类型：string\n   * @param trendIndex? 所查询的趋势类型\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function category_trend(nodeId: string, trendIndex?: \"SalesCount\" | \"BrandProductCount\" | \"SellerProductCount\" | \"AvgPrice\" | \"AvgRatingCount\" | \"AvgScore\" | \"NewProductSalesAmountShare\" | \"AmazonSalesAmountShare\" | \"Top3ProductSalesAmountShare\" | \"Top3BrandSalesAmountShare\" | \"Top3SellerSalesAmountShare\", amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询类目的nodeid，数据类型：string\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"trendIndex\": {\n            \"description\": \"所查询的趋势类型\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"SalesCount\",\n              \"BrandProductCount\",\n              \"SellerProductCount\",\n              \"AvgPrice\",\n              \"AvgRatingCount\",\n              \"AvgScore\",\n              \"NewProductSalesAmountShare\",\n              \"AmazonSalesAmountShare\",\n              \"Top3ProductSalesAmountShare\",\n              \"Top3BrandSalesAmountShare\",\n              \"Top3SellerSalesAmountShare\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"SalesCount\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台上实时热搜关键词榜，按周搜索量排序\n   *\n   * @param rank_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量排名大于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param rank_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量排名小于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param search_volume_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月搜索量大于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param search_volume_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月搜索量小于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\n   * @param keywordSupportSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function keyword_list(rank_min?: number, rank_max?: number, search_volume_min?: number, search_volume_max?: number, page?: number);\n  // optional (1): keywordSupportSite\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"rank_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量排名大于等于此值的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"rank_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量排名小于等于此值的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"search_volume_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月搜索量大于等于此值的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"search_volume_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月搜索量小于等于此值的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"keywordSupportSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询沃尔玛电商平台**指定类目**的**实时**销量Top100产品数据报告\n   *\n   * @param nodeId 细分类目nodeId，查询这个指定细分类目数据\n   */\n  function walmart_category_report_by_node_id(nodeId: string);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"细分类目nodeId，查询这个指定细分类目数据\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 亚马逊平台上单个产品分析报告\n   *\n   * @param asin 产品asin码\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function product_report(asin: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"asin\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品asin码\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"asin\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台产品类目结构\n   *\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function category_tree(amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询沃尔玛电商平台上电商平台上热搜关键词详情\n   *\n   * @param keyword 查询的关键词\n   */\n  function walmart_keyword_detail(keyword: string);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"keyword\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台上产品的详情数据\n   *\n   * @param asin 产品ASIN，仅支持单ASIN查询\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function product_detail(asin: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"asin\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品ASIN，仅支持单ASIN查询\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"asin\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询沃尔玛电商平台上热搜关键词的延伸词关键词，可用于卖家查询相关关键词、发现长尾词或挖掘个性化需求\n   *\n   * @param keyword 查询的关键词\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\n   */\n  function walmart_keyword_extends(keyword: string, page?: number);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"keyword\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 按名称搜索Tiktok上相关类目市场，返回类目市场名称和nodeid\n   *\n   * @param searchName 搜索的产品名称\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_category_name_search(searchName: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"搜索的产品名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"searchName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询产品在Tiktok平台上的相似产品，可用于分析此类产品的销售情况\n   *\n   * @param searchName 查询的产品名称\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_similar_product(searchName: string, page?: number, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的产品名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"searchName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 获取当前时间\n   */\n  function get_time();\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {}\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台上历史日期的热搜关键词榜，按周搜索量排序\n   *\n   * @param date 所查询的时间，格式yyyy-MM-dd，最早支持2025-03-04\n   * @param rank_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量排名大于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param rank_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量排名小于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param search_volume_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量大于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param search_volume_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选周搜索量小于等于此值的关键词\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据\n   * @param keywordSupportSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function keyword_list_from_history(date: string, rank_min?: number, rank_max?: number, search_volume_min?: number, search_volume_max?: number);\n  // optional (2): page, keywordSupportSite\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"date\": {[... 23247 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778322291109}}
{"type":"message","id":"60ec34ee","parentId":"fe934f7f","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:25:11.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full schema. Let me analyze what Sorftime MCP can do and how it maps to the SOP:\n\nPlatforms covered:\n- **Amazon** (multiple sites: US, GB, DE, FR, IN, CA, JP, ES, IT, MX, AE, AU, BR, SA)\n- **TikTok Shop** (US, MY, PH, VN, ID, GB)\n- **Walmart** \n- **1688** (alibaba)\n\nKey tools for the SOP's three tracks:\n1. **TikTok Shop data**: `tiktok_category_report`, `tiktok_similar_product`, `tiktok_product_video`, `tiktok_product_trend`, `tiktok_author`, `tiktok_category_name_search`\n\n\n2. **Amazon and 1688 data**: `ali1688_similar_product` for product sourcing, plus various Amazon tools for category trends and keyword research\n3. **Walmart data**: Category reports and keyword tools available if needed\n\nFor the东南亚+TikTok focus, the TikTok tools and Amazon multi-site support are particularly valuable for the product strategy.\n\nNow comparing against the SOP requirements: TikTok Shop data is covered across seven countries including the Southeast Asian markets, 1688 sourcing is available, and Amazon covers all the needed sites. However, Mercado Libre isn't supported—though since the SOP focuses on TikTok Shop and Amazon for product discovery, that might not be critical. Let me examine what's actually available for the core Southeast Asian markets like VN, PH, ID, and MY.\n","thinkingSignature":"4c23f576aa0522c43915b84b31926260c0936ae050a70bcda45b1e08a88fe694"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nKey 更新成功，看看它能覆盖什么：\n\n**平台支持：**\n| 平台 | 覆盖站点 | 对应 SOP 轨道 |\n|------|---------|--------------|\n| **TikTok Shop** | VN, PH, MY, ID, US, GB | 第一轨（主动选品） |\n| **Amazon** | US, GB, DE, FR, JP, MX... 14个站 | 参考/竞品分析 |\n| **1688** | ✅ | 第三轨（供应链驱动） |\n| **Walmart** | ✅ | 暂无需求 |\n| **Mercado Libre** | ❌ | - |\n\n**跟 SOP 选品流程的对应：**\n\n- ✅ `tiktok_category_report` → 获取类目销量/趋势数据（参数卡死用）\n- ✅ `tiktok_similar_product` → 找相似品（跟品策略）\n- ✅ `tiktok_product_trend` → 产品多维度趋势（评分维度）\n- ✅ `ali1688_similar_product` → 找1688货源（算进货价）\n- ✅ `search_categories_broadly` → 亚马逊细分类目选品（多维约束）\n\n**Mercado Libre 没有** — 不过 SOP v5.0 已经完全转向 TikTok 东南亚了，这个不影响。\n\n**现在要测吗？** 用一两次试试看数据格式能不能直接进评分流程，比如搜一个越南TikTok类目看看返回什么。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11608,"output":614,"cacheRead":28288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778322291113,"responseId":"064e3e7358d8bdc0e951c9d9eefdcc33"}}
