{"type":"message","id":"dac17e42","parentId":"ea17a563","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:26:21.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the image - it's a screenshot of the Sorftime MCP configuration page. The key `sutbzf...ut09` is masked and has expired. The user was showing me this to confirm that the old key is expired. The new key `zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09` has already been configured.\n\nThis is just confirming the old key status. I already updated the key, so this screenshot is just for reference. I should acknowledge this and confirm the new key is in place.\n","thinkingSignature":"7748e7d662d12bcacbcc3217eb918b67b76cff1efdd444259c22ecdb0dc16896"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了，这是 Sorftime MCP 的管理界面，确认旧 key（`sutbzf…ut09`）过期了。\n\n新 key 已经配好了（`zwpmsmv…`），健康状态 ✅，有 17 个工具可用，覆盖：\n\n- TikTok Shop（VN/PH/MY/ID/US/GB）\n- Amazon（14个站点）\n- 1688\n- Walmart\n\n晚上拿到 100 次试用 key 直接开测就行。现在这个是永久的但只有基础功能。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":166,"output":218,"cacheRead":34496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34880,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778322371823,"responseId":"064e3ec41c420c33321779e0f2ab09e5"}}
