{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50c4f9bb54a8c4a05651d2d3dfc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-09 18:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"7391cda1","parentId":"7fe01a56","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:26:26.962Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"e6010a00","parentId":"7391cda1","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:26:40.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the trial key has only 3 days and 100 calls. So the \"zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09\" key is the 3-day/100-call trial key. We should use it wisely to test the most important capabilities.\n\nThe key tools for our SOP are:\n1. TikTok Shop - for first track (主动选品)\n2. 1688 - for third track (供应链驱动)\n\nLet me think about how to use the 100 calls strategically. We should test the most important data points that feed into our scoring system.\n\nKey things to test with the 100 calls:\n\n\n1. TikTok category search and category report for Vietnam (VN) - maybe 5-10 calls\n2. TikTok similar product search - 5-10 calls  \n3. 1688 product search - 5-10 calls\n4. Testing the data format\n\nI should suggest they save most of the calls and use them strategically, or we could just run a few tests now to see what the data looks like before committing to a full test plan.\n","thinkingSignature":"8690efe779a3be9908ce7dbd08bcaaaa5b6afdef7d33d30ae2538eca2645374a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n那就省着用，先测关键链路。我建议这样分配 100 次：\n\n**核心测试（20-30次）：**\n- TikTok 越南站类目搜索 + 类目报告 × 3\n- TikTok 相似产品搜索（发饰相关）× 3\n- 1688 同款搜索 × 3\n- 拿到的数据格式验证\n\n**剩下的留着正式跑选品流程用。**\n\n要现在先跑一个试试看数据格式吗？比如搜个发饰类目看返回什么。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1404,"output":344,"cacheRead":33216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34964,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778322386962,"responseId":"064e3ed4fb43c83c9d3f9bc44c2cea12"}}
