{"type":"message","id":"dc81df59","parentId":"914fdb5a","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:28:05.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there's only SKILL.md and references/ in the plugin directory. The feishu-doc skill uses a `feishu_doc` tool. I need to check how to use it. Let me look at the feishu wiki skill since the link is to a bitable (which might be wiki-based).\n\nActually looking at the URL: `https://my.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd?table=tblHU2do30jzinJT&view=vewigQOcAI`\n\nThis is a Feishu Bitable (多维表格), not a docx. The skill mentions `feishu_wiki` but I'm not sure if that covers bitables too.\n\n\nThe feishu plugin handles bitable access, so I should try reading the Bitable schema and then attempt to list records from the table to see what data's available.\n","thinkingSignature":"990ba3366efad5ee8c662bd587d8074fa0c895e1b5b961e90b4c1b3ccee9e7cc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xhq8enyipc5d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw tools list 2>/dev/null | grep -i feishu"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":174,"output":232,"cacheRead":36096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36502,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778322474861,"responseId":"064e3f2bef05615181d231a6f4e99253"}}
