{"type":"message","id":"0fb24013","parentId":"ee278e77","timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:56:06.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has updated the SOP, now claiming that Sorftime MCP has TikTok full interface + 1688 search interface. But from the schema I pulled earlier, I didn't see `ali1688_product_search` or `tiktok_product_influencer_analysis` or `tiktok_product_trend`.\n\nLet me re-check the Sorftime schema more carefully to see if there are any methods I missed that could match these.\n\nActually, let me re-call the schema to see the full list - the output was truncated at 23247 characters. Let me see if there's a way to get more methods.\n\nActually, looking at the schema output again, it was truncated. But from what I could see, the methods available were:\n\n\n- `tiktok_category_name_search` and `tiktok_category_report` for TikTok data\n- `tiktok_similar_product` and `tiktok_product_trend` - though I'm not entirely sure `tiktok_product_trend` was actually in the truncated output\n- `similar_product_feature` for Amazon\n- `product_report`, `product_detail`, `category_tree`, `category_trend`, and keyword-related methods for Amazon\n- `keyword_list`, `keyword_list_from_history`, and `keyword_search_results` for keyword and product data\n- `walmart_category_report_by_node_id`, `walmart_keyword_detail`, `walmart_keyword_extends`, `walmart_keyword_list`, and `walmart_get_favorite_keyword` for Walmart\n- `get_favorite_keyword`, `get_time`, and `NotAuthorization` rounding out the list\n\nI'm not seeing the 1688 or influencer analysis methods the user mentioned, so either they're new additions, the user is mistaken about what's available, or they're in the truncated portion I haven't seen yet. I should re-check the full schema to confirm.\n","thinkingSignature":"92624109a7a1ea926cd60f18d9ca36d22fbcadba56988966a0a8a5b01d641143"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t648myy5zv8k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter list sorftime-mcp --schema 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"1688\\|influencer\\|ali\\|trend\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62796,"output":429,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63225,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778331344908,"responseId":"064e61d112ba81afc66b6632ff99cd7b"}}
