{"type":"message","id":"d6d3b443","parentId":"9496cb3a","timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:56:43.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the actual Sorftime MCP tools:\n\nAvailable for TikTok:\n- `tiktok_author` - search for creators/authors\n- `tiktok_category_name_search` - ✅ has\n- `tiktok_category_report` - ✅ has\n- `tiktok_product_detail` - product details\n- `tiktok_product_trend` - ✅ has (product trend)\n- `tiktok_product_video_author` - videos/authors for a product\n- `tiktok_product_video` - videos for a product\n- `tiktok_similar_product` - ✅ has\n\nFor 1688:\n- `ali1688_similar_product` - ✅ has (search 1688 by product name)\n\n\nThe SOP requires `tiktok_product_influencer_analysis`, but that's not available—though `tiktok_product_video_author` might provide similar creator data. I can work around the missing influencer tool by adapting the workflow, and since `tiktok_product_trend` exists, I can use that to extract the trend data needed for the analysis.\n\nSo the real gaps are just the influencer-specific endpoint and possibly the 1688 search tool. Let me start by executing the SOP as designed and working around these limitations where needed.\n","thinkingSignature":"c52f792fc9ab055f77e08a58bc807f0041e9ad9cdbb9295e6435ee098df0d9a7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，更新一下能力盘点：\n\n**SOP vs 实际工具对照：**\n\n| 步骤 | 需要的 | 实际有 |\n|-----|-------|--------|\n| `tiktok_category_name_search` | ✅ | ✅ |\n| `tiktok_category_report` | ✅ | ✅ |\n| `tiktok_similar_product` | ✅ | ✅ |\n| `tiktok_product_trend` | ✅ | ✅ |\n| `tiktok_product_influencer_analysis` | ❌ | ⚠️ 有 `tiktok_product_video_author` 可替代 |\n| `ali1688_similar_product` | ✅ | ✅ |\n\n**缺口就一个**：`tiktok_product_influencer_analysis` 没有，但 `tiktok_product_video_author` 可以拿到带货达人和视频数据，能做类似分析。\n\n**开始跑 SOP Step 1？** 双站类目扫描（VN+TH各2次），先把类目增长率摸清楚，再决定是否深入。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":546,"output":446,"cacheRead":63360,"cacheWrite