{"type":"message","id":"a697a6ee","parentId":"3f51b913","timestamp":"2026-05-09T13:37:43.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"MY works! VN works. TH doesn't. It seems specifically the TH site is failing. Let me try a few more things with TH to see if maybe it's a transient error or if the tool itself is having an issue with Thailand specifically.\n","thinkingSignature":"89422ba62662c21eef0410fd1f2651a3c86bba8f0dfd7e9c08acca962e6fd3ae"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nMY ✅，VN ✅，TH ❌ — 看起来是 TH 这个站点的接口本身有问题，不是调用频率或权限。\n\n先跑通 VN 全流程，TH 回头单独排查。\n\n**继续 Step 1（VN）：**\n\n- ✅ `tiktok_category_name_search` → nodeId `908552`\n- ⏳ `tiktok_category_report`（已测过，上一轮用了1次）\n- ⏳ `tiktok_similar_product` → 获取产品列表\n\n下一步：用 VN 的 nodeId `908552` 跑 `tiktok_category_report` 看看增长率，再跑 `tiktok_similar_product` 拿50个产品。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":221,"output":187,"cacheRead":66048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66456,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778333853492,"responseId":"064e6b9da9ce2e41abb015d43bae5815"}}
