{"type":"message","id":"7f91e679","parentId":"37d884b6","timestamp":"2026-05-09T13:41:16.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The 1688 data came back perfectly. Now I have all three pieces working:\n1. TikTok category report ✅\n2. 1688 similar product search ✅\n\nNow let me calculate if a product from the TikTok top50 has good profit potential with 1688 sourcing.\n\nLooking at the data:\n- Top1: \"Kẹp Chuối\" - 月销量 10768, 价格 $17000 VND (~$0.68 USD), 评论 2819\n  - This is too high volume - NOT low基数\n\nLet me focus on finding LOW volume, HIGH growth products from the category report data. The SOP says:\n\n\n- 总销量 < 500\n- 评论数 < 100\n- 近7天新增达人 > 10\n- 近7天新增视频 > 20\n- 售价 $5-$22\n\nThe category report only shows Top50 products. I need to look for smaller products. Let me check - looking at the data I already pulled, the smallest volume products are:\n- 2221, 2408, 2425... all above 500\n\nSo the category report only shows top products. I need another way to find the smaller products. Maybe `tiktok_similar_product` would give me a different set that includes smaller products.\n\nBut wait - the category report showed `月销量: 391523` with `上线3个月内新品数量: 25` and `上线3个月内新品月销量和: 24567`. That means there are 25 new products in the last 3 months with total monthly sales of 24567, averaging about 983 per product - still above my 500 threshold.\n\nLet me reconsider what I'm looking at. The SOP wants products with total volume under 500 and under 100 reviews - these would be genuinely new, small products. The `tiktok_category_report` only surfaces the top performers, so I need a different approach to find products that meet these stricter criteria. me re-read... \"近7天新增达人>10, 近7天新增视频>20\" - these are fields in `tiktok_product_trend`. But I need to GET `tiktok_product_trend` to know if a product qualifies. The screening criteria are:\n- 近7天新增达人 > 10\n- 近7天新增视频 > 20\n- 总销量 < 500\n- 评论数 < 100\n- 售价 $5-$22\n\nSo I need to call `tiktok_product_trend` to verify each product. But calling it for 50 products would cost 50 calls just for step 2.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. The user said \"只要有链接，我就能通过链接进行选品上架erp\" - meaning they just need the links. So the goal is really just finding valid TikTok product links and matching them with 1688 sourcing options, not necessarily running through the entire SOP verification workflow. I should focus on getting products with TikTok links that can be sourced from 1688. Looking at the new products in the category, most exceed the 500 sales threshold. The data shows only 25 new products emerged in the past three months, which is quite limited for finding low-competition items. I should pivot toward using `tiktok_similar_product` to discover smaller products that haven't yet dominated the category.\n","thinkingSignature":"b083e4a7c18c6a83a9c73e6c87d84bcc22893d273005e0234c37dd2c7a848fff"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n1688 接口通了 ✅ 现在链路完整了。\n\n类目报告里有个关键数据：`上线3个月内新品数量: 25`，但这些都是月销 983+ 的，不符合\"低基数\"标准。\n\n**要找真正低基数（<500销量）的新品，得换 `tiktok_similar_product` 接口扫。** 但 50 个产品逐个查 `tiktok_product_trend` 消耗太大。\n\n**换个思路直接跑：**\n\n我现在已经有：\n- ✅ TikTok 类目报告（VN Hair Clips Top50）\n- ✅ 1688 货源匹配接口\n- ✅ 飞书写入能力\n\n**最快验证链路：用现有 Top50 里挑一个低评分的品，搜 1688 同款，直接写进飞书表格。**\n\n比如从 Top50 里找一个评论少、增速正的新面孔，匹配 1688 货源，直接输出可上架的链接包。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7eebly9hhnmm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 找 Top50 里评分低(新)、增速正、评论少、销量不太高的品\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_similar_product searchName=\"hair clip claw\" site=VN page=1 2>/dev/null","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5771,"output":965,"cacheRead":73728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778334033727,"responseId":"064e6c52929149d1c0e8366a71d9754b"}}
