{"type":"message","id":"7c4664de","parentId":"33de15d5","timestamp":"2026-05-09T13:41:59.509Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'm getting results from `tiktok_similar_product`. Now I need to identify products that meet the SOP's criteria for \"low base high growth\" small products:\n\n**SOP criteria:**\n- 近7天新增达人 > 10\n- 近7天新增视频 > 20\n- 总销量 < 500\n- 评论数 < 100\n- 售价 $5-$22 (but prices here are in VND, so I need to convert)\n\nLooking at the results, the prices are in VND (Vietnamese Dong), not USD. $5-$22 would be roughly 125,000 - 550,000 VND.\n\nBut the results I'm getting show \"评论数量\" (review count) and \"月销量\" (monthly sales). However, I need the 7-day new influencers and 7-day new videos data, which would come from `tiktok_product_trend`. \n\n\nI can see a couple of promising candidates from the similar products list: one with just 8 reviews and 2839 monthly sales at 9000 VND (around $0.36), and another with 3 reviews but 1996 monthly sales at 100000 VND (around $4). Neither quite hits the mark though.\n\nI should shift tactics—instead of diving deeper into individual product analysis, let me focus on the broader workflow. The real value here is linking TikTok products to 1688 inventory, which I already confirmed works. Let me test that connection with one of these products to establish the full pipeline.\n","thinkingSignature":"e2013c286367c9b9adb6d548fe0be6e4dc4410f9076f919ebea66314d155e869"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**已确认链路通！**\n\n- ✅ TikTok 产品搜索 + 类目报告\n- ✅ 1688 同款搜索（已验证，返回链接/价格/卖家）\n- ✅ 飞书表格写入（已验证）\n\n1688 那个关键词 `kẹp tóc đuôi ngựa` 搜出了 50 条结果，价格 ¥0.7~12.5，支持代发链接都有。\n\n**全链路跑通了，核心就差：产品ID → 1688关键词匹配 → 利润计算 → 入库。**\n\n我来给你演示一个完整案例，直接挑一个潜力品匹配 1688：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5n4hpo3mal4d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_product_trend productId=1729984590540998833 site=VN 2>/dev/null","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":